OL,6,FThe CCN's membership of 37 councils,
OL,7,Fwhich serve 47% of the population in
OL,8,FEngland, received #240 million of the
OL,9,Fextra government funding for 2024/25
OL,10,Fbut are planning in-year savings of
OL,11,Fmore than #1 billion.
OL,13,FThese councils, a mix of county and
OL,14,Funitary authorities, are said to be
OL,15,Fstill facing a collective funding gap
OL,16,Fof #1.1 billion over the next two
OL,17,Fyears.
