OL,6,FMr Corcoran said, while the additional
OL,7,Ffunding provided by the government
OL,8,Fwould make a tangible difference and
OL,9,Fprotect services, the fragile state of
OL,10,Fcouncil finances means council tax
OL,11,Fbills had to rise to ensure
OL,12,Fsustainability.
