OL,3,CCouncil tax to rise by maximum amount
OL,4,Cin nearly all areas
OL,6,FMr Corcoran added: "No council leader
OL,7,Ftakes the decision to raise council
OL,8,Ftax lightly as we know this will add
OL,9,Fto the cost of living for residents,
OL,10,Fbut councils have had little choice
OL,11,Fbut to put up council tax due to the
OL,12,Fincreased demands, particularly in
OL,13,Fchildren's services.
OL,15,F"The next government must set out a
OL,16,Flong-term funding plan for councils
OL,17,Fwhile also undertaking a comprehensive
OL,18,Freform programme to help drive down
OL,19,Fcosts, especially for children's
OL,20,Fservices and home-to-school transport."
