OL,3,CCouncil tax to rise by maximum amount
OL,4,Cin nearly all areas
OL,6,FSome councils have agreed on the
OL,7,Fmaximum increase but plan to introduce
OL,8,Fmeasures to mitigate the impact on
OL,9,Fresidents, such as making support-
OL,10,Ffunding available to low-income
OL,11,Fhouseholds.
OL,13,FThe CCN said councils in county areas
OL,14,Fget 67% of their funding from council
OL,15,Ftax, which is above the 56% average
OL,16,Ffor all upper-tier councils with
OL,17,Fsocial care responsibilities.
