OL,6,FFor some county local authorities, up
OL,7,Fto 80% of their funding comes from
OL,8,Fcouncil tax because they receive lower
OL,9,Fgovernment grants than other areas,
OL,10,Fthe CCN added.
OL,12,FCouncils are said to be making savings
OL,13,Fby boosting preventative measures in
OL,14,Fchildren's and adult social care, but
OL,15,Fthis approach will take time to have
OL,16,Fan impact on finances.
